00:08:19.824 --> 00:08:20.740
I love a pulp natural.

00:08:20.740 --> 00:08:21.890
[LAUGHTER]

00:08:21.890 --> 00:08:24.840
All three of you guys,
I'd really like to know.

00:08:24.840 --> 00:08:26.330
JAMES MCLAUGHLIN: Yeah.

00:08:26.330 --> 00:08:28.790
SAM SABORI: I honestly think
you can make great coffee

00:08:28.790 --> 00:08:30.767
on any device, it's
just, how much time do

00:08:30.767 --> 00:08:31.850
