00:09:27.900 --> 00:09:31.350
So the Chemex tends to
be my method of choice,

00:09:31.350 --> 00:09:34.706
and I bring it back and share it
with my neighbors where I sit.

00:09:34.706 --> 00:09:37.080
It's a little bit unforgiving
sometimes, hard to dial in.

00:09:37.080 --> 00:09:39.960
I've done a lot more work
with the Kalita lately.

00:09:39.960 --> 00:09:41.030
